Package nist.model

Class Entry

java.lang.Object
nist.model.Entry
public class Entry extends Object
Represents an Entry for a vulnerability in the NIST data feed. Each entry contains detailed information about a specific vulnerability, including its severity, impact, exploitability, and affected software.

This class supports operations for tracking, comparing, and describing vulnerability data entries.

Since:
2024-05-01
Version:
